                    },
                    "body": "This works now with the new datasets API:\r\n\r\n{code}\r\nIn [21]: dataset = ds.dataset(\"notebooks-arrow/test_empty_dir/\")                                                                                                                                                   \r\n\r\nIn [22]: dataset.schema                                                                                                                                                                                            \r\nOut[22]: \r\n\r\nIn [23]: dataset.to_table().to_pandas()                                                                                                                                                                            \r\nOut[23]: \r\nEmpty DataFrame\r\nColumns: []\r\nIndex: []\r\n{code}\r\n\r\nSo once we use the datasets API under the hood in pyarrow.parquet (ARROW-8039), this issue should be solved (might want to add a test for it)",
